nding increase in the price of cigarettes when excise duties go up.{\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s13\sl240\slmult1\ql{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch{\*\cs68\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up8\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch  }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f2\fs20\lang7177\i0\b0 See T6770 and Econex (1), paragraph 175 (Expert Witness Bundle, pages 158.10-158.11).}}}
