\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li1440\ri0\lin1440\rin0\fi-360\af2\afs22\lang7177\af0\af4\afs20\lang1025\sl276\slmult1\qj\af3 \u61623\'3f\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s16\sl276\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls1\li1440\ri0\lin1440\rin0\fi-360\rtlch\af4\afs20\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af0\langfe255\hich\f2\fs22\lang7177\loch\f2\fs22\lang7177{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f2\fs22\lang7177\i0\b0\rtlch The category manager\'92s task is to promote the category as opposed to merely promoting its own brands.  This it will do by ensuring that the retail display \'91communicates\'92 effectively with the customer by conveying accurate and accessible information.  This 
