. }}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f2\fs22\lang7177\i0\b0 However because retail outlets cater for literally thousands of categories of products, the retailer cannot be expected to understand detailed aspects pertinent to the marketing of each category.  This detailed know-how is said to be the preserve of the 
