, because of limited visibility in retail outlets, their perceived availability.\'92}}}}
{\*\cs68\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up9\rtlch\af11\afs24\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af9\langfe255\hich\f0\fs24\lang1033\loch\f0\fs24\lang1033\rtlch\af2 }{\rtlch\af2   Alternatively \'96 and rather eccentrically \'96 it has been suggested, certainly where the payments made to the HORECA venues are concerned, that BATSA\'92s level of payment are driven by a raising rivals cost strategy in which is purposefu
