r of the retailers and the key HORECA venues }{\rtlch\af2\ltrch\dbch\hich\i\loch\i vis a vis}{\rtlch\af2  the manufacturers, including BATSA, and is inconsistent with the notion that BATSA enjoyed the freedom to do with the cigarette category what it wanted.}}
