countertop.  He testifies further that only after PMI secured this for its Marlboro brand was he approached by JTI.}{\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s13\sl240\slmult1\ql{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af4\afs20\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af0\langfe255\hich\f2\fs20\lang7177\loch\f2\fs20\lang7177{\*\cs68\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up8\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch  }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f2\fs20\lang7177\i0\b0 Cited in closing argument T7268-9}}}
