\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li284\ri0\lin284\rin0\fi-360\f2\fs22\lang7177\f0\fs22\f4\fs20\lang1025\sl276\slmult1\qj 180.\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s4\sl276\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls2\li284\ri0\lin284\rin0\fi-360\rtlch\af4\afs20\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af0\langfe255\hich\f2\fs22\lang7177\loch\f2\fs22\lang7177{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f2\fs22\lang7177\i0\b0\rtlch Because of the relative autonomy enjoyed by Spar franchisees, approaches to cigarette merchandising within the various Spar stores range over a significant spectrum. For example certain of the stores use BATSA-provided merchandising furniture, while others
