\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li284\ri0\lin284\rin0\fi-360\f2\fs22\lang7177\f0\fs22\f4\fs20\lang1025\sl276\slmult1\qj 181.\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s4\sl276\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls2\li284\ri0\lin284\rin0\fi-360\rtlch\af4\afs20\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af0\langfe255\hich\f2\fs22\lang7177\loch\f2\fs22\lang7177{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f2\fs22\lang7177\i0\b0{\rtlch But of critical importance, it appears that while the trade investment agreement is concluded between the franchisor and the BATSA head office, individual stores are not thereby precluded from entering into independent agreements with other suppliers. Whil
