\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s16\sl480\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-709\rtlch\af4\afs20\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af0\langfe255\hich\f2\fs22\lang7177\loch\f2\fs22\lang7177{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f2\fs22\lang7177\i0\b0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\b\loch\b BATSA\'92S Trade Investment Agreements \'96 HORECA}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s16\sl480\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-709\rtlch\af2\afs20\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af0\langfe255\hich\f2\fs22\lang7177\loch\f2\fs22\lang7177 
\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li295\ri0\lin295\rin0\fi-360\f2\fs22\lang7177\f0\fs22\f4\fs20\lang1025\sl276\slmult1\qj 242.\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s1\sl276\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls2\li295\ri0\lin295\rin0\fi-360\rtlch\af4\afs20\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af0\langfe255\hich\f2\fs22\lang7177\loch\f2\fs22\lang7177{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f2\fs22\lang7177\i0\b0\rtlch There are two promotional opportunities afforded by HORECA venues.  The first is at the cigarette distribution sites in these venues.  These venues increasingly distribute cigarettes through vending machines placed in the premises by agreement with one or 
other of the vending machine operators (VMOs).  It is alleged that BATSA incentivises both the VMOs and the venue owners in order to secure privileged space allocations and positioning in, and branding opportunities on, the vending machines.}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\sl276\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-709\rtlch\af2\afs20\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af0\langfe255\hich\f2\fs22\lang7177\loch\f2\fs22\lang7177 
\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li295\ri0\lin295\rin0\fi-360\f2\fs22\lang7177\f0\fs22\f4\fs20\lang1025\sl276\slmult1\qj 243.\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s1\sl276\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls2\li295\ri0\lin295\rin0\fi-360\rtlch\af4\afs20\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af0\langfe255\hich\f2\fs22\lang7177\loch\f2\fs22\lang7177{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f2\fs22\lang7177\i0\b0\rtlch Secondly, the cigarette companies host promotional events at which direct marketing and other methods that brand the venue are employed in order to encourage trial of the brand being promoted and, more generally, to associate the venue and the type of clie
ntele it attracts with a particular cigarette brand.  JTI and the Commission allege that BATSA is entering into exclusive arrangements with venue owners, the coverage of which effectively forecloses its rivals from promotional events at HORECA venues. }
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s16\sl480\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-709\rtlch\af2\afs20\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af0\langfe255\hich\f2\fs22\lang7177\loch\f2\fs22\lang7177 
\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li295\ri0\lin295\rin0\fi-360\f2\fs22\lang7177\f0\fs22\f4\fs20\lang1025\sl276\slmult1\qj 244.\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s1\sl276\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls2\li295\ri0\lin295\rin0\fi-360\rtlch\af4\afs20\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af0\langfe255\hich\f2\fs22\lang7177\loch\f2\fs22\lang7177{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f2\fs22\lang7177\i0\b0\rtlch While the applicants have sought to link these mechanisms of promotion \'96 that is, the VMO display and the promotional events \'96 they can clearly be distinguished for the purpose of assessing the extent of foreclosure, if any, arising from BATSA\'92s alleged co
nduct.  We will explore the linkages between the vending machines and the promotional events where appropriate.}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s16\sl480\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-709\rtlch\af2\afs20\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af0\langfe255\hich\f2\fs22\lang7177\loch\f2\fs22\lang7177 
