s with desirable entertainment venues.}}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f2\fs22\lang7177\i0\b0{\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s13\sl240\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch{\*\cs68\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up8\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch  \'91}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f2\fs20\lang7177\i0\b0 Desirable\'92, as we shall elaborate, appears on the cigarette manufacturers\'92 reckoning to exclude \'91main market\'92 venues,  Again we point out that these are venues frequented by large numbers of Camel smokers, and, as noted above, significantly more cigarett
