\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li295\ri0\lin295\rin0\fi-360\f2\fs22\lang7177\f0\fs22\f4\fs20\lang1025\sl276\slmult1\qj 267.\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s1\sl276\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls2\li295\ri0\lin295\rin0\fi-360\rtlch\af4\afs20\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af0\langfe255\hich\f2\fs22\lang7177\loch\f2\fs22\lang7177{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f2\fs22\lang7177\i0\b0{\rtlch For its part, PMI managed to secure }}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f2\fs22\lang7177\i0\b0{\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\i\loch\i Ignite, }{\rtlcha premier venue in Camps Bay, at the beginning of 2006.  It thus became a Marlboro branded venue. In 2007 PMI increased its offer by 20% in the face of BATSA competition.}{\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s13\sl240\slmult1\ql{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch{\*\cs68\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up8\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch  }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f2\fs20\lang7177\i0\b0 T5232}}}
